[ACTIVITY] 合約簽署流程

[ACTOR] Admin -> {specs/actors/Admin.md}
[ACTOR] Customer -> {specs/actors/Customer.md}
[ACTOR] System -> {specs/actors/System.md}
[ACTOR] WooCommerce -> {specs/actors/WooCommerce.md}

[STEP:1] @Admin {features/contract-template/儲存合約模板公司章.feature}
[STEP:2] @Admin {features/settings/更新外掛設定.feature}

[STEP:3] @Customer {features/contract/建立合約.feature}
[FORK:3a]
  [PARALLEL:3a] @System {features/contract/寄送合約通知信.feature}
  [PARALLEL:3a] @Customer {features/contract/簽署完成顯示Modal.feature}
[JOIN:3a]

[DECISION:3b] 合約審核結果？
  [BRANCH:3b:核准] @Admin {features/contract/核准合約.feature}
  [BRANCH:3b:拒絕] @Admin {features/contract/拒絕合約.feature}
[MERGE:3b]

[STEP:4] @Admin {features/contract/批量變更合約狀態.feature}

[STEP:5] @Admin {features/contract/合約列表.feature}
[STEP:6] @Admin {features/contract/查看合約詳情.feature}

[DECISION:6a] WooCommerce 是否啟用？
  [BRANCH:6a:啟用] @Admin {features/woocommerce/訂單中查看合約.feature}
  [BRANCH:6a:未啟用] {specs/ui/無WooCommerce.md}
[MERGE:6a]

[STEP:7] @Customer {features/woocommerce/我的帳號查看合約.feature}

[END]
